    <string name="faq_q5">How do I make a purchase?</string>
    <string name="faq_a5">When you find a product you want to purchase, tap it to view the product details, check the price, description, and available options, then tap Add to Cart and continue through checkout.</string>
    <string name="faq_q6">What payment methods are accepted?</string>
    <string name="faq_a6">We currently support saved cards, cash on delivery, and the payment methods enabled on your device.</string>
    <string name="faq_q7">Can I cancel or return an order?</string>
    <string name="faq_a7">You can request cancellation before dispatch. Once delivered, you can start a return request from customer service.</string>
    <string name="faq_q8">How can I contact customer support for assistance?</string>
    <string name="faq_a8">Open Help Center to chat with customer service, call support, or use one of our social channels.</string>
    <string name="faq_q9">How do I change my account details?</string>
    <string name="faq_a9">Open My Details from the Account tab, update your information, then press Submit to save it locally on your device.</string>
